      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your dedication and selflessness have clearly touched many, but it's important to remember that people can't pour from an empty cup. Feeling burdened despite your kindness is a heavy load to bear. It might help to express these feelings to Mark and Jenny. Perhaps setting boundaries and enlisting additional support could help distribute the care responsibilities and alleviate the exhaustion. Taking care of yourself is not self-centered, it's necessary and it's okay. Is there someone who could be a part of your support network?",
      "source": "target",
